snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000 Space Marine 2 Official Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2024
snippet.description: Join us live on June 20th, at 6PM CEST | 12PM EDT | 9AM PDT to take a deep dive into Space Marine 2's gameplay mechanics and learn more about the campaign, co-op and PvP modes.
